                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17151012-40-off187 t17151012-40-cd189"></join> last, in the Night-time
            </rs>. It was very plain the Prosecutor's House was broke open, and the Goods gone; and the Prisoner being suspected, his House was search'd, and some of them found there, and others at one Walker's, by the Prisoner's Directions, who then confess'd the Fact; but upon his Trial, denied it. The Jury found him <rs id="t17151012-40-verdict190" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17151012-40-verdict190" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
